  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2665150/extras/6712ab9296c67d6c2133155d0cf63ef0.avif?t=1733678926\" width=615 height=180 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🔗 Join Our Community! 🔗</h2>Connect on Discord for the latest updates, community events, and an engaging space to share your experiences!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2665150/extras/2036962197ab3271d8b62ee5754e11db.avif?t=1733678926\" width=614 height=76 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🌱 Craft Your Unique Ecosystem 🌱</h2>Unleash your creativity and design a vibrant ecosystem. Mix and match from a rich selection of fauna, flora, and unique decorations to infuse your personal touch into every corner.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2665150/extras/78f061443cdef6b6027c6c6ab9ba64b9.avif?t=1733678926\" width=614 height=76 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🌲 Cultivate Beauty and Bounty 🌲</h2>Plant an array of trees that not only add to the aesthetic appeal but also enrich your ecosystem with essential resources and habitats.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2665150/extras/d9eafdfc792211c256e0c2ebd832689d.avif?t=1733678926\" width=614 height=76 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🐾 Breathe Life Into Your World 🐾</h2>Introduce a variety of animals into your ecosystem and witness the enchanting interactions among them and with their environment.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2665150/extras/44e521ced593d0fbbec8d15a5681184a.avif?t=1733678926\" width=614 height=76 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🛠️ Dynamic Ecosystem Maintenance 🛠️</h2>Adapt and respond as your ecosystem evolves. Weather changes and animal behaviors will challenge you to maintain balance and harmony.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2665150/extras/65437e236e7f54253660141884f9525f.avif?t=1733678926\" width=614 height=76 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🔍 Unlock the Secrets of Nature 🔍</h2>Embark on a journey to discover new environments, intriguing animals, and exotic plants. Each discovery unlocks the potential for even more diverse ecosystems.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2665150/extras/6712ab9296c67d6c2133155d0cf63ef0.avif?t=1733678926\" width=615 height=180 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🔗 Join Our Community! 🔗</h2>Connect on Discord for the latest updates, community events, and an engaging space to share your experiences!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2665150/extras/2036962197ab3271d8b62ee5754e11db.avif?t=1733678926\" width=614 height=76 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🌱 Craft Your Unique Ecosystem 🌱</h2>Unleash your creativity and design a vibrant ecosystem. Mix and match from a rich selection of fauna, flora, and unique decorations to infuse your personal touch into every corner.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2665150/extras/78f061443cdef6b6027c6c6ab9ba64b9.avif?t=1733678926\" width=614 height=76 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🌲 Cultivate Beauty and Bounty 🌲</h2>Plant an array of trees that not only add to the aesthetic appeal but also enrich your ecosystem with essential resources and habitats.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2665150/extras/d9eafdfc792211c256e0c2ebd832689d.avif?t=1733678926\" width=614 height=76 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🐾 Breathe Life Into Your World 🐾</h2>Introduce a variety of animals into your ecosystem and witness the enchanting interactions among them and with their environment.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2665150/extras/44e521ced593d0fbbec8d15a5681184a.avif?t=1733678926\" width=614 height=76 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🛠️ Dynamic Ecosystem Maintenance 🛠️